    . X . X . |
    X . . . X |
    X X X X X |
    X . . . X |
    X . . . X |
    X . . . X |
    X . . . X |;


letter a  ( 5x7)
    . . . . . |
    . . . . . |
    . X X X . |
    . . . . X |
    . X X X . |
